Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God’s Mercy
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God Alone Is Good
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God’s Justice
---
By Him Who holds my soul, if ye did not sin, verily would Allâh do away with
you, and bring forth a people who sin and who ask forgiveness of Allâh, and
them would He forgive.
